						<svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="16" rx="2" stroke="#DFFF00" stroke-width="1.6"></rect><path d="M3 9h18" stroke="#DFFF00" stroke-width="1.6"></path><path d="M8 14h5" stroke="#DFFF00" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg>
					</span>
